Enum ItemLabelAnchor

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ItemLabelAnchor>
org.jfree.chart.labels.ItemLabelAnchor
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ItemLabelAnchor>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum ItemLabelAnchor extends Enum<ItemLabelAnchor>
An enumeration of the positions that a value label can take, relative to an item in a CategoryPlot.
